score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:45:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即場食都算賄賂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接受左就係接受左</blockquote><br />\n唔當架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7947d2ce5a474c6b57a64705517b7a9a8bef2a","tid":404165,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"即場食加食緊嘅時間零宣傳都係賄選?"},{"pid":"3421fa98734fa0dd3020a778438a514e9cd627c5","tid":404165,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:48:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bccef65b404d576aba790d3e57dfcb8b5249b3ac","tid":404165,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://portal.gov.mo/web/guest/info_detail?infoid=517570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fportal.gov.mo%2Fweb%2Fguest%2Finfo_detail%3Finfoid%3D517570&d=dfVp40sK0uRlKjoKzgMyZRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=5fee088b\" target=\"_blank\">http://portal.gov.mo/web/guest/info_detail?infoid=517570</a><br />\n<br />\n廉政專員張永春簡歷<br />\n<br />\n張永春，一九六六年九月出生於北京，已婚，北京外國語大學文學學士，澳門大學法學學士。<br />\n<br />\n曾任登記局局長及公證員助理、物業登記局局長、司法事務局局長，二零零零年十一月至二零一四年十二月任法務局局長。曾為司法援助委員會主席、公共行政改革諮詢委員會委員、法律改革諮詢委員會委員。"},{"pid":"081ef10048763ecc4d1e612d05b93931cf1aa468","tid":404165,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T02:56:03.000Z","msg":"免費早餐 又廉又正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://apm.safp.gov.mo/external/chin/apm/files/205/logo/CCAC1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapm.safp.gov.mo%2Fexternal%2Fchin%2Fapm%2Ffiles%2F205%2Flogo%2FCCAC1.gif&h=5507e56e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a974cf32f7fea6283b6c76331456398a3aa971f7","tid":404165,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"50步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f7b2ee40c39b4de307b57f76a2d4a4c9c4808b","tid":404165,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"班廢老扮哂勁嘅至理名言其中一句就係: 世界上無免費嘅午餐<br />\n<br />\n下次可以答番佢: 早餐有，係澳門，遲d早午晚三餐都一定有"}]}